column11: as of May 2019, HAI computation is based on Freddie Mac 30-year fixed rate mortgage contract rates.NAR calculates the 30-year effective fixed rate based on Freddie Mac's 30-year fixed mortgage contract rate, 30-year fixed mortgage points and fees, and a median loan value based on the NAR median price and a 20 percent downpayment.
